the trial has attracted international attention due to mayekisos 
position as general secretary of the national union of metalworkers 
of south africa and because many activists view the prosecution as 
an attempt to stifle peaceful antiapartheid activity 
conditions of bail bar the defendants from entering alexandra 
addressing meetings or granting press interviews 
