any member of the public he said 
the nebraska court said trahans challenge must fail in light of 
the may decision 
garbage left for collection at a designated location and 
accessible to the public shall not be accorded constitutional 
protection whether it is on or off someones private property the 
state court ruled 
the case is trahan vs nebraska 88697 
