ii and was in omaha for christmas before the victory march in new 
york 
oldfield said no one has tried to buy the heart but that the 
guinness book of world records has called about it 
they found somebody with a 36yearold cake in storage and they 
were toying with the idea of a strange category that would include 
such things but nothing came of it he said 
