a million homeless and the threat of infection and disease 
at hoffmannla roche where two regional sales managers are of 
armenian descent the effort has taken on special meaning 
it really brings it down to a personal level knowing these 
people have relatives there said kassy mcgourty a spokeswoman 
for the nutleybased pharmaceutical company 
