21 1987 that included 77 billion in new loans restructured 
437 billion of the debt and decreased interest rates on 86 
billion loaned in 198384 
petriccioli 60 also worked out mexicos purchase of several 
billion dollars worth of its foreign debt certificates at discount 
rates this year and helped enforce a solidarity pact of 
government business and labor that helped lower annual inflation 
from 1509 percent in 1987 to about 48 percent in 1988 
by keeping interest rates high and the pesos value virtually 
steady against the dollar petriccioli also managed to accumulate an 
alltime record of 16 billion in foreign currency reserves last 
year 
