<TEXT>
 
rain man 
 
the autistic savant syndrome has been used to describe a 
spectacular skill or talent that occurs in an autistic or retarded 
child it might seem a likely subject for a diseaseofthemonth 
television movie instead it is the theme of a motion picture 
rain man which is the most original and compelling american 
drama since one flew over the cuckoos nest 
yes its a drama though as in cuckoo there are hearty 
laughs essentially its the saga of two longlost brothers seeking 
a reconciliation against heavy odds 
cruise is a rapacious wheelerdealer trying to make a bundle by 
importing sports cars in los angeles his major deal is interrupted 
by news that his father from whom he was long estranged has died 
in cincinnati cruise attends the funeral and learns he has been 
disinherited his fathers 3 million estate has been placed in 
trust 
but for whom cruise is astounded to learn that he has an older 
brother hoffman who has been institutionalized most of his life 
cruise decides to virtually kidnap the brother and fight the will in 
california 
hoffman may seem like an automaton but he has a superhuman way 
with numbers this pays off at the blackjack table in las vegas 
that helps ameliorate cruises rage and he begins to understand and 
cope with his brother 
no good to give away all the plot suffice to say that the 
inspired script by ronald bass and barry morrow based on morrows 
story offers a wealth of surprises both comedic and dramatic 
barry levinson tin men good morning vietnam directs 
in masterful style it is his best effort in what promises to be a 
distinguished career he maintains a beautiful balance between the 
harddriving cynical cruise and the childlike hoffman 
hoffmans performance is astounding he gets inside the skin of 
raymond babbitt and never allows him to become monotonous or 
pitiable cruise dashing in his risky business shades carries 
a heavy load talking at a fast clip as the car dealer and as the 
exasperated brother struggling to communicate with raymond cruise 
has emerged as a superb actor as well as teenage heartthrob 
valerina golino is excellent as cruises understanding 
girlfriend jerry molen injects humanity into his role as raymonds 
guardian 
mark johnson produced the united artists film which is rated r 
mostly for cruises expletives running time 130 minutes 
by bob thomas associated press writer 
</TEXT>
