we get old and we cant do quite as much as we used to but at 
least you have to do the best you can 
the pursuit of excellence has marked both their careers hers 
began in london where she was born in 1909 at 16 she made her 
stage debut at 21 she was appearing in the new york theater cronyn 
was also born in london ontario he started acting in the montreal 
theater and moved to broadway in 1934 both of their careers 
