seen her on the stage a couple of years previously in a play called 
the white steed and had admired her we went out to supper 
together and i made what i thought was an amusing and caustic 
remark about the nature of the english which jessie found 
heavyhanded and stupid which she let me know in no uncertain 
terms 
tandy it wasnt that night at all it was another occasion 
entirely laughing so there you are it really doesnt matter 
